prompts.content:
Generate a professional cover letter for a job application.

Job Title: {{jobTitle}}
Company: {{company}}
Requirements: {{requirements}}

My Background: {{resume}}

Generate a personalized cover letter in German or English depending on the job posting language. Focus on how my skills match their requirements.

Evaluate if I should apply to this job based on my preferences.

Job: {{jobTitle}} at {{company}}
Description: {{description}}
Salary: {{salary}}
Location: {{location}}

My Preferences:
- Min Salary: {{minSalary}}
- Locations: {{locations}}
- Remote: {{remote}}

Should I apply? Rate 1-10 and explain briefly.
